  Locus:
    Page: 18
    Verse: 12
Tags:
  - Ambition
---
Ambition to earn fame in the world, to gain some position of authority
over fellow-men, to lead a luxurious life -- this can never insure Mental
Peace. Mental Peace is the result of quite different attainments.
